divs: sighting detailscase #34825 on 1-15-12 @ 4:11pm i had a phone interview with a witness who on 10-27-11, during his nightly walk observed a stationary\hovering object on the horizon with blinking lights at about 25\30 degrees and 1\4-1\2 miles from his location. the reason he noticed the object was because it had bright lights. the approximate time of the sighting was 20:30. the object was hovering low over the hills sw of his location. the night was dark and clear and the sky full of stars. witness claims to always "look up" at the sky. living on a flight path, the sky is always full of commercial aircraft. witness watched the object for several minutes before it "vanished in a blur". witness claims to have had many sightings. multiple sightings have been reported on the mufon site by the witness.
Summary: Witness observed craft with blinking lights while taking a walk
